    <string name="faq_q1">What is Goat Insurance?</string>
    <string name="faq_a1">Goat Insurance is a protection plan that helps you in case of death of your insured goat due to accidents, diseases or natural calamities. You will receive compensation as per the policy terms and conditions.</string>
    <string name="faq_q2">How do I register my goat for insurance?</string>
    <string name="faq_a2">You can register via the app by providing farmer and goat details, and uploading photos.</string>
    <string name="faq_q3">What documents are required for registration?</string>
    <string name="faq_a3">Aadhaar card, farmer details, and clear photos of the goat from different angles are required.</string>
    <string name="faq_q4">How can I check my policy status?</string>
    <string name="faq_a4">Go to the \'Goat List\' or \'Policy\' section in your dashboard to view active and expired policies.</string>
    <string name="faq_q5">How do I file a claim?</string>
    <string name="faq_a5">Report the goat\'s death immediately through the app, upload photos, and Didi will visit for verification.</string>
    <string name="faq_q6">How long does claim approval take?</string>
    <string name="faq_a6">Usually, it takes 7-10 working days after the verification is completed by the coordinator.</string>
    <string name="faq_q7">What is the claim settlement ratio?</string>
    <string name="faq_a7">We have a high claim settlement ratio as the process is transparent and assisted by Suraksha Didis.</string>
    <string name="faq_q8">Can I cancel my policy?</string>
    <string name="faq_a8">Yes, policies can be cancelled within a specific period. Please contact support for assistance.</string>
